name: ZBot.infosheet
description: Collection: virus.uwu This collection consists a series of 3 pieces, each one is the representation of a computer "virus" (malware) that had a significant impact on the internet. The Trojan virus is mainly distributed through unauthorized downloads, phishing schemes and spam campaigns posing as organizations such as Facebook or Microsoft, trying to get the user to visit a website using a link to infect the computer.
